{"tid":1641154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又係代post : 有關11月區選（文長）","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:31.000Z","uid":205289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4359f7dcf85c73a3f048996753f75e4907d549e","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"首先，我想阻各位少少時間去睇吓近期政府嘅<br />\n<br />\n布局。<br />\n<br />\n時勢發展至今日，反蒙面法、緊急法、實彈射<br />\n<br />\n擊...種種唔應該發生嘅事都一一出現，相信大<br />\n<br />\n家好清楚背後都係建制派興風作浪，可能你會<br />\n<br />\n話：唓！唔使你講、低能嘅都知啦！講埋晒啲<br />\n<br />\n癈話！區選贏硬呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你有咁嘅諗法，我怕到時會輸得好慘。還<br />\n<br />\n記得200萬人上街之後，爆出麥美娟問候林太嘅<br />\n<br />\n錄音，直指有200萬選民會令建制輸到底褲都<br />\n<br />\n無、但係今時今日黨鐵配合政府嘅情況呢？黨<br />\n<br />\n鐵又關咩區選事呀？要知道選民有三種人：草<br />\n<br />\n根、富豪同中產，基本上除咗中產、其他都歸<br />\n<br />\n晒邊，咁嘅情形下，就要爭取呢群游離選民嘅<br />\n<br />\n支持。你諗諗嗰200萬人有幾多中產？<br />\n<br />\n而777政府同建制深明得中產、得天下，所以用<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵、交通運輸搞鳩班中產，等佢地經濟受影<br />\n<br />\n響，再屈落抗爭者度，咁班中產嘅票唔多唔少<br />\n<br />\n都會去咗對面。<br />\n<br />\n我想你地知道，當時有200萬人呢個數，對家好<br />\n<br />\n驚之餘，已經做好對策，而且無一刻放鬆過。<br />\n<br />\n所以，請各位今後思考吓行動係咪有利於運<br />\n<br />\n動。"},{"pid":"ab120df3dbf5de9bde12e2e2b62d89ab36c730e4","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"83bcaa2ec1eb27cf048982cecb35812253858f09","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1b79fa10be33c0f88dfa8a95a34723b0d32e7c78","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"bf0ded2b8d54e8cb50691822464f158f010724dd","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"96fb129d74409324c0b0934a63d6d5c9211b7826","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"15c9836e6630bef75bc3ec9f8075dbe16139bf87","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"6465411f4886042aaaa3ed222f10fadd3598fbf6","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"254f14939823952eb3570f38aa8faf4091dc7f2b","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"e49b6f07e4c32f53dfa9b27190a590429f4b3874","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"c8b1d6f605ad573d6bfe5394fa0699ebbbce653b","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"efb6f31c5ed4463087b35ad7383b643fac8d41f7","tid":1641154,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"輕鬆十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}